---
title: Smart Double Turkey Crunch Salad with Peanuts and Edamame
description: Crunchy coleslaw mix and crisp bell peppers add fun to every bite of this salad. Soy and mirin combine in a sweet, sticky glaze that dresses lean ground turkey and protein-rich edamame.

